data.eml:eml: Stenomastigus pseudofranzi sp. n., from South Africa (Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jałoszyński, Paweł (2012): Stenomastigus pseudofranzi sp. n., from South Africa (Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae). Zootaxa 3268: 55-62, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.212300
